    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The Oath of the Watchers binds paladins to protect mortal realms from the predations of extraplanar creatures, many of which can lay waste to mortal soldiers. Thus, the Watchers hone their minds, spirits, and bodies to be the ultimate weapons against such threats.</p><p>Paladins who follow the Watchers' oath are ever vigilant in spotting the influence of extraplanar forces, often establishing a network of spies and informants to gather information on suspected cults. To a Watcher, keeping a healthy suspicion and awareness about one's surroundings is as natural as wearing armor in battle.</p><h3>Oath of the Watchers Spells</h3><table><thead><tr><td><strong>Paladin Level</strong></td><td><strong>Spells</strong></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3rd</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.T6nNBhzyjOKZ0ueS]{Alarm}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.5NxrFVxMFPiXb4oI]{Detect Magic}</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.Su395UdYgfEzImSJ]{Moonbeam}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.MQKLylFDEgABYUvl]{See Invisibility}</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.fRhxAiPjKGsYpuNO]{Counterspell}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.Flvf6rp4o4qythcn]{Nondetection}</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.6jP2are19bkyqrR5]{Aura of Purity}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.NtdmlSBrs1mCCgQi]{Banishment}</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.R6HwuSHAkPV4kAzF]{Hold Monster}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-spells.yacJyg7wuVIGvoWk]{Scrying}</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Oath of Vengeance Features</h3><p>3rd: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.q7mkuLHXU4VRJMaN]{Tenets of the Watchers}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.FB9y8GIagrtTe6bC]{Watcher's Will}, @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.uCcsMH3REjmFAOoy]{Abjure the Extraplanar}</p><p>7th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.oiYwi4bd2iChYqcz]{Aura of the Sentinel}</p><p>15th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.WKYMgCiC4COP4FDW]{Vigilant Rebuke}</p><p>20th: @UUID[Compendium.5e-complete.5e-class-features.R5fU3ugTRclKr4VX]{Mortal Bulwark}</p>",
